The Advanced Theory of Social Organism: The Ancient Wisdom of Five Chinese Imperial Baths 

by Peter He

This is a sociological book will help reader to build a complete worldview and realize the society actually is a tree from several important aspects. After reading this book ,reader will have a better comprehension on the encountered people and the purpose of their actions. This book is valuable for the young and has a great guiding significance.
